HEADWORD: Simoon
<hw>Si*moon"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar. <ets>sam<?/m</ets>, fr. <ets>samma</ets>
to poison. Cf. <er>Samiel</er>.]</ety> <def>A hot, dry, suffocating,
